{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But little did they-- when they came to the conclusion that we are not heeding their advice or command or however you'd want to take it, they rammed the ship.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rammed the ship.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The British.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They rammed the ship, tearing out a hole into the body of the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The water went in and people were standing until here in water, the people that were on the lowest deck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- before-- I forgot something to tell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before that evening, the captain knew most probably from further-- from before experience.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took-- [SIGHS] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what they-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot a word in English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That we put that around so the English couldn't get a hold on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sometimes you have-- on borders you have-- from-- wire that has--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took barbed wire, we put around that they couldn't jump onto the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it didn't take them long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had the children organized on the side of the ship, with tins, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tins of meat or whatever it was, just conserves, when they will attack us, to throw that in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, there was a battle that was maybe 1 and 1/2 to 2 hours, until the English just threw in tear gas and we didn't see anything before our eyes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had taken from tires-- they had the inside of a tire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had put it here on their arms, and with a baton so that nobody could hit them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The English put down like a bit of a tire, like part of a tire, put inside-- it was probably they had wood there to hold it-- so that nobody could-- you throw a tine and it just-- just doesn't harm you.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had batons.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
